    "Furthermore, P4 and P11 avoided using unnecessary large models for tasks that could be carried out by smaller and less energy-hungry models.",
    "Consultant P11 used this example: \"If we know that questions can be answered with GPT 3.5 Turbo as well, which is a lighter model than GPT 4, then we can use GPT 3.5 Turbo.\"",
    "Lastly, the most mentioned practice was to not overuse AI (P3, P7, P10).",
    "Co-Founder P7 said the following about this: \"We see AI in general as a tool.",
    "Once you have a hammer, not everything is a nail."
